# AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus

**Enumeration**

The statuses for sample buffer rendering.

## Declaration

```swift
enum AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus
```

## Status values

- **AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.unknown**: The object doesn’t have any sample buffers enqueued.
- **AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.rendering**: The object is rendering the sample buffer.
- **AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.failed**: The object can no longer render sample buffers because of an error.

## Initializers

- **init(rawValue:)**

## Determining rendering status

- **status**: The status of the audio renderer.

## Conforms To

- BitwiseCopyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- RawRepresentable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
